definition: to add/to attach/to be close to/to be attached
band/belt/girdle/ribbon/tire/area/zone/region/CL:條|条[tiao2]/to wear/to carry/to take along/to bear (i.e. to have)/to lead/to bring/to look after/to raise
collateral damage (both as a legal term, and as a military euphemism)

sentences.english: Unlike those of the West, Chinese loans are "no strings attached."
sentences.chinese: 不象西方国家，中国的贷款是“无附带条件”。

sentences.english: Other pad irons not to be supplied along with equipments shall be provided by the bidder.
sentences.chinese: 设备未附带的其它垫铁由投标人提供。

sentences.english: Incidentally, here's a good piece of news.
sentences.chinese: 附带告诉你一个好消息。

sentences.english: It also comes jam-packed with premade code snippets for common CSS styles.
sentences.chinese: 它还附带果酱与常见的CSS样式代码段预制包装。

sentences.english: Brain Freeze now only affects your frost damage spells with chilling effects.
sentences.chinese: 大脑冻结现在只影响附带寒冷效果的冰系伤害法术。

sentences.english: This software is sold or published without their source code.
sentences.chinese: 这种软件出售或发布时并没有附带源代码。

sentences.english: Our code is in the solutions folder on the CD included with this book.
sentences.chinese: 我们的代码在本书所附带光盘中的解决方案文件夹中。

sentences.english: There is an increase in the occurrence of collateral damage during the course of our operation.
sentences.chinese: 我方执行任务其间，附带性破坏的发生次数上升了。

sentences.english: This kind of previous job is accessary .
sentences.chinese: 这种事先的准备工作是附带进行的。

sentences.english: The chairman accompanied his speech with gestures.
sentences.chinese: 会议主席作讲演时附带做着手势。

sentences.english: There are also four adapters to charge some popular brand mobile phones.
sentences.chinese: 另外附带四个转接头可以连接大多数品牌手机。

sentences.english: If aid is out of humanity, why should it be given with proviso ?
sentences.chinese: 西方的援助如果真的是出于人道，为什么要附带条件？

sentences.english: The radio that came with the Evader worked just fine.
sentences.chinese: 附带强制收兑的无线电工作就好了。

sentences.english: The book is not only new but also with a small disk.
sentences.chinese: 书并不旧并且附带小盘，欣喜之余特做此证明。

sentences.english: HBL Revision 99 comes with some major improvements.
sentences.chinese: 宏宝修订99附带一些重大改进。

sentences.english: If you use chlorine tablets or iodine tablets, follow the directions that come with the tablets.
sentences.chinese: 如果你使用氯片或碘片，遵照药片附带的指示使用。
